next

public final com.sun.ws.management.server.EnumerationItem next()
Supply the next element of the iteration. This is invoked to satisfy a Pull request. The operation must return within the timeout specified in the Pull request, otherwise release will be invoked and the current thread interrupted. When cancelled, the implementation can return the result currently accumulated (in which case no Fault is generated) or it can return null in which case a TimedOutFault is returned.

Specified by:
next in interface com.sun.ws.management.server.EnumerationIterator
Returns:
an Element that is used to construct a proper response for a PullResponse.
